Package: MassiveMDS
Title: Massively Parallel Multidimensional Scaling Library
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    c(person("Marc A.", "Suchard", email = "msuchard@ucla.edu", role = "aut"),
    person("Andrew J.", "Holbrook", email = "aholbroo@g.ucla.edu", role = c("aut","cre")))
Description: Facilitates fast Bayesian MDS through GPU, multi-core CPU, and SIMD vectorization powered implementations of the Hamiltonian Monte Carlo algorithm. The package may be built either as a standalone library or as an R package relying on Rcpp.
